name: Martha Oilcloth Tote Bag
description: The very popular oilcloth cloth tote bag from Love Lammie. Made in very pretty floral Martha matt oilcloth. Wipe clean for easy care. One external pocket and one very handy inside pocket perfect for holding purses,keys, etc. Black zip closure. Straps that fit perfectly on your shoulder. Making this the perfect everyday bag! 38 x 12 x 30cm. This bag is on special offer!!

name: Oilcloth Wash Bag
description:
Another best seller from Love Lammie. Our folding oilcloth wash bags are the the ultimate in wash bags. They have three separate compartments perfect for holding lotions and potions. Choose from  gorgeous mat vintage inspired Collette,Mabel floral stripe or Issy red spot oilcloth and trimmed with  very pretty bindings.

They opens our flat making them just perfect for packing in your suitcase, with a loop to hang and a button to fasten. Wipe clean for easy care.

59 x 25cm open, 25 x 21cm closed
